These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Job: security-guard, scientist, videographer, engineer
Flower: iris, daisy, poppy, lily
1. Flower:lily is on the left of Job:videographer##1
2. Job:security-guard is on the left of Flower:daisy##1
3. Job:engineer is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:poppy is on the left or right of Flower:lily##3
5. Job:security-guard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Job   | security-guard | scientist | engineer | videographer |
| Flower        | iris | daisy   | lily | poppy    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
House: wooden, townhouse, cape-cod, tower
Flower: daisy, zinnia, iris, orchid
1. House:townhouse is on the left of House:tower##1
2. Flower:daisy is on the left of Flower:iris##1
3. Flower:iris is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:daisy == House:wooden##1
5. Flower:zinnia is on the right of Flower:iris##1
6. Flower:daisy == House:wooden##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | cape-cod | wooden  | townhouse  | tower |
| Flower   | orchid    | daisy | iris | zinnia    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: puzzles, dancing, singing, writing
Beverage: cola, mirinda, almond-milk, fanta
1. Hobby:writing is on the left or right of Beverage:fanta##3
2. Hobby:singing is in an even position##4
3. Beverage:fanta is on the left or right of Hobby:dancing##3
4. Beverage:fanta is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
5. Beverage:cola is in an odd position##4
6. Hobby:dancing is on the right of Hobby:singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Hobby          | writing | singing | dancing    | puzzles      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | fanta     | cola | mirinda |

