.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
City: berlin, london, nizza, rome
Sport: golf, cricket, skiing, parkour
1. City:nizza is on the right of Sport:parkour##1
2. Sport:cricket == City:rome##1
3. Sport:skiing is on the right of City:berlin##1
4. City:london is on the far left##1
5. City:nizza is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:golf is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| City   | london  | berlin    | nizza   | rome       |
| Sport   | golf | parkour | skiing | cricket |

