.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
Movie-Genre: crime, disaster, family, drama
Birthday: august, october, may, february
1. Birthday:february is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:disaster##3
2. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
3. Birthday:february is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:drama##3
4. Movie-Genre:drama is on the right of Birthday:february##1
5. Movie-Genre:crime is between Movie-Genre:drama and Movie-Genre:disaster##2
6. Birthday:october is in an odd position##4
7. Birthday:october is between Movie-Genre:crime and Birthday:may##2
8. Movie-Genre:crime is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:disaster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | crime      | drama | family |
| Birthday   | august  | february | october    | may            |

