2. Color:white is on the right of Color:coral##1
3. Movie-Genre:epic is between Movie-Genre:superhero and Color:pink##2
4. Movie-Genre:epic is in an odd position##4
5. Color:pink == Movie-Genre:thriller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | aquamarine | coral   | white | pink |
| Movie-Genre    | romance     | superhero | epic     | thriller  |

