2. City:miami is on the right of Pet:goldfish##1
3. City:colone is between City:miami and Pet:bird##2
4. Pet:goldfish is in an odd position##4
5. City:colone is on the left or right of City:miami##3
6. Pet:snake is on the left or right of City:paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
