.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
City: paris, liverpool, san-francisco, boston
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, townhouse, art-deco
1. City:liverpool is in an even position##4
2. City:liverpool is on the left or right of House:ranch-style##3
3. House:gothic-revival is between City:paris and House:ranch-style##2
4. City:liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
5. House:townhouse is on the right of City:boston##1
6. House:townhouse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| City         | paris | san-francisco   | boston | liverpool |
| House   | art-deco          | gothic-revival | ranch-style         | townhouse  |

 